      "content": "wait r u serious?? that sounds so extreme... i really don't think it's that bad. i've had cramps like this before and they just go away with heat or meds. plus i cant afford an er visit right now, it's like hundreds of dollars. can i just try taking an extra dose of the ibuprofen to see if it helps? if i can just dull the pain enough to sleep, i'll be fine in the morning. it's probably just nothing.",
